## Compatible Tankmates

**Excellent companions:**
- **[Molly Fish](/species/molly-fish)** — Similar water preferences; both hard-water livebearers
- **[Corydoras](/species/corydoras)** — Note Corydoras prefer slightly softer water; compromise at neutral pH
- **[Guppy](/species/guppy)** — Compatible; Guppies are somewhat more flexible on hardness
- **[Bristlenose Pleco](/species/bristlenose-pleco)** — Peaceful bottom-dweller
- Swordtails — Compatible but will hybridise; keep separate if maintaining colour lines

**Avoid:**
- Soft-water blackwater species (Discus, Cardinal Tetras, Bettas in optimal setups)
- Aggressive cichlids
- Large predatory fish

